member.name: P:Employment.Services.ReferenceData.Contract.AutocompleteAddressResponseV1.Id
member.summary: The address identifier of the address
member.remarks: The address identifier is used within the iGas dataset as a short term primary key. As such the identifier should only be used for lookups occuring in relation to the same activity
